I have a few spots in mind. You trust me?
Dinner at Diablo Burger. Juicy stacks of red meat
while staring at a juicy stack with red hair...
And great conversation too, the commiseration only two
people bound to a diabolical evil force can share.
The evening continues with taking in the sunset on Vesper
Beach, the soft sounds of the waves punctuating long,
meaningful looks that say more than words ever could...
The last stop of the night comes at the Serpent's Sway,
Vesper's hottest nightclub. Proudly taking in the jealous
looks of other patrons, the velvet ropes part and the
couple enters to the pounding club music.
